## Asset Compilation

### Development

In development, assets are served directly without compilation:

```bash
# Start Rails server (assets served automatically)
rails server

# Assets available at:
# http://localhost:3000/assets/logo.png
# http://localhost:3000/assets/application.css
```

### Production

Compile assets before deployment:

```bash
# Compile assets for production
rails assets:precompile

# Output:
# public/assets/logo-abc123456.png
# public/assets/application-def789012.css

# Clean old compiled assets
rails assets:clobber

# Clean then precompile
rails assets:clean assets:precompile
```
